Release Notes for Version 3.12.0
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.12.0 is the 1st release in the Errata Tool 3.12 development period.
It closes [30 bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release of Errata Tool includes an API for managing CDN repos, fixes
related to incorrect released package lists, partner notifications for
previously embargoed advisories, "readonly-admin" access for all users, plus a
number of other bug fixes and improvements.

